content: Very bad version. Don't download this one.
Love this game!!! Which it had roller ball controls

Just about as bad as it gets. The controlls are so bad it's so slow moving that it's just about unplayable. Nothing like the original as far as game play goes.
Pretty good but lacking original game sound and some original game features. Fun but not quite there.
Does not work with bluetooth gamepad (joystick)
impossible controls, and doesn't have features of original game.
it's OK, It's a lot like the orginal eccept for the controls. The controls suck. Other than that it's a fun game.
looks like defender, but gameplay is something much simpler. landers rarely pick up men.

The controls are what we used to call "dibby"..... Meaning they suck! The response of the ship is absolutely terrible. The thrust is off and the ship gets stuck! The look of the game brings back the memories but to real old school Defender champions this is a good attempt but that controls responsiveness and dynamics need work! Got my refund on this one but I'll check back and see if any improvements were made, then I'll buy it back!
Like the game very similar to original but slower.My only issue is after completing attack wave 5 the game always crashes?
Controls let the game down. Far too slow

Looks the same as the original but controls could do with making faster  as it's very slow to move the ship plus bit of a put off with the layout being on the screen as it takes up half of it with the movement tabs.
Very accurate to tha coinop version my only complaint is that controls
